<para style="q1">

<verse number="14" style="v" />May his ancestors' sins be mentioned to Yahweh;</para>

<para style="q1">and may the sin of his mother not be forgotten.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="15" style="v" />May their guilt always be before Yahweh;</para>

<para style="q1">may Yahweh cut off their memory from the earth.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="16" style="v" />May Yahweh do this because this man never bothered to show any covenant faithfulness,</para>

<para style="q1">but instead harassed the oppressed, the needy,</para>

<para style="q1">and the disheartened to death.</para>
